		<div class="story-heads">
		<h1>Maggie Haberman, Eve Babitz, Daniel Kraus, and more: 21 new books out today!</h1>
			</div>
	</div>
										<div class="byline-date">
					<span class="byline"><a href="https://lithub.com/author/juliahass/"  title="Julia Hass">Julia Hass</a></span>
					<span class="hr"></span>
					<span class="date">June 23, 2026</span>
				</div>
						<div class="story-body">
								<p style="text-align: left;">The most perfect day in June, as in: my birthday! Happy June 23rd to all, and especially the authors and readers of the below collection of new titles. There&#8217;s a comprehensive, insiders’ account of the presidency of he-who-shall-not-be-named-on-my-birthday, as well as a treasure trove of both sent and unsent letters from Eve Babitz. There&#8217;s a new book by Pulitzer Prize-winner Daniel Kraus, and many fun works of fiction otherwise: by Cay Kim, Elisa Faison, and even Danny McBride. Read on for the full list, and happy Tuesday!</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">*</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" data-attachment-id="272943" data-permalink="https://lithub.com/maggie-haberman-eve-babitz-daniel-kraus-and-more-21-new-books-out-today/screenshot-2026-06-11-at-11-11-27-am/" data-orig-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/Screenshot-2026-06-11-at-11.11.27-AM.png" data-orig-size="1042,1572" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="Regime Change, Maggie Haberman" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-large-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/Screenshot-2026-06-11-at-11.11.27-AM-679x1024.png" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-272943" src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/Screenshot-2026-06-11-at-11.11.27-AM-199x300.png" alt="Regime Change, Maggie Haberman" width="199" height="300" srcset="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/Screenshot-2026-06-11-at-11.11.27-AM-199x300.png 199w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/Screenshot-2026-06-11-at-11.11.27-AM-679x1024.png 679w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/Screenshot-2026-06-11-at-11.11.27-AM-768x1159.png 768w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/Screenshot-2026-06-11-at-11.11.27-AM-40x60.png 40w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/Screenshot-2026-06-11-at-11.11.27-AM-1018x1536.png 1018w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/Screenshot-2026-06-11-at-11.11.27-AM-33x50.png 33w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/Screenshot-2026-06-11-at-11.11.27-AM.png 1042w" sizes="(max-width: 